Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:36.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was reunited with the young man\nat my friend's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:41.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His soul, which does not know\nwhat it means to love another,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:45.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...was profoundly shaken by one\Nwho does know what it is to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He asked, "Do you love\nyour fiancée?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:59.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My life is a hollow,\nfragile thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.37,0:02:20.87,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should give some more\Nthought to my marriage to Eugenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:23.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:27.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not sure if I really\nlove her or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:29.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:37.06,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's been\nbothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:41.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,First you go through the motions.\NThen the emotions will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:42.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:50.78,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Albert, a messenger from the\NCount of Monte Cristo said to deliver this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:52.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,From the Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Invitations to the opera...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.24,0:02:59.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"As luck would have it, I managed to secure\nan open box at the opera house."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.49,0:03:02.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"If you like, would you care\nto join me this evening?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"By all means, please bring\nyour fiancée."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:10.13,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine how there could be\nany open boxes at the opera house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:11.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:14.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but could you\ndeliver this to Eugenie?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:17.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, you're going\nto deliver it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:22.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Considerate little touches like\Nthis will win her over little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:25.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:28.40,count fo,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,352)}Act 6:\NHer Melancholy, My Melancholy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wake her\nthis morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is Monsieur Debray here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:41.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes Mademoiselle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Mademoiselle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:49.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.\NIs Mother still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.67,0:03:51.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mademoiselle,\nit looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:14.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Eugenie.\NYou're as lovely as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You spent the night, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father, your soup\nis getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. I trust you\nslept well last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Thank you for\nyour hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,\nabout Olympus Trading...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.19,0:04:53.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's a valuable piece of information... Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:05:02.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I give appropriate compensation to those\nwho give me information before anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.66,0:05:05.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not in a hurry, would you care\nto join us for breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for\nthe invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was on my way to give\NEugenie her ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:29.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am on my way to visit Baron Danglars\nto see to some business negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:33.61,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a lucky coincidence!\NPlease, allow me to introduce you to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.15,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is indeed an unexpected\nstroke of good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:39.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are many things at their estate\Nthat you will find interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:43.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, if you have time, you should\nask them to show you the stables.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:48.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Madame Danglars has a horse named Eclipse\nthat is the finest in all of Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:55.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This way, Messieurs. If you will wait\nin the parlor for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:56.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:59.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lucien! What brings you here\nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I had my hands full\nwith this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie!\NGood morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:11.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A man has to play\nhis cards right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.23,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:16.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count! Do me the honor of allowing me\nto invite you to my home next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:17.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me,\NI'll stop by your room later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.50,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle, Olympus Trading\nhas started to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pretend to prop it up,\nand then make it fall even farther!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:44.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Further buying is inadvisable.\NIt is below the insolvency line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:48.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care. Wait until it hits bottom,\Nand then buy them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:49.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:54.27,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A few hundred investors are gonna\nhang themselves over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:59.36,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur, the Count of Monte Cristo\nis waiting in the parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He is, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle, have the credit\nassessment results...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...for this Count of Monte Cristo\nperson come in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:07.95,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Out of three investigatory agencies,\ntwo rate him as AA+,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:09.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and the third rates him\nas AAA.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His peerage title is valid,\nas well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bet. He probably paid a lot\nof money for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry to\nkeep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:22.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here,\ntoo, Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:26.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Baron.\NThis is the Count of Monte Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:28.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had hoped to put in\na good word for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:34.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His Excellency mentioned that\nhe doesn't have a bank,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:38.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...so I thought I should introduce\nhim to you, Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was most considerate\nof you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always glad to meet\nfine new customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:48.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce Baron Danglars, the\nmost powerful banker in Paris right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.91,0:07:52.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It is a pleasure to make\nyour acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you missed a spot\nover here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:01.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You need to be more careful\nwith Eclipse's grooming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And never give him anything\nbut the feed I've specified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Madame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:12.10,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've received a letter of introduction\nand contract papers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...from the firm of Thomson & French.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:18.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I'm amazed that they\nwould act as guarantor for an individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:22.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They are the largest banking firm\nin Eastern Space.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:28.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed they are. However, there is one\nitem in this contract that concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:30.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That concerns you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:35.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,According to this, no upper limit\nhas been set to your line of credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.04,0:08:38.96,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In short, it could be interpreted\nthat my bank...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:41.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...would have to indefinitely\ncontinue to provide you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:44.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...with any amount you wished,\nno matter how great the sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And does that present\na problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a bit of an\nawkward situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:56.73,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You say it as if it were nothing, but such\nlopsided deals don't exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:09:01.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Be that as it may, the firm of Thomson & French\nhave judged that in my case, they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:05.32,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you don't doubt the\nvalidity of this contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:10.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all, its authenticity has already\Nbeen verified. This contract is genuine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:13.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. In which case,\nyou are saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:17.16,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that it is me that you\nare unable to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.47,0:09:35.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got tickets to tonight's\nopera from the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:38.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About that Count of Monte Cristo fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he managed to secure\na box at the opera house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:46.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's quite a skilled player.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:52.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go pay our respects\Nduring intermission tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:58.12,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:09:59.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,F-Five hundred million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:06.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had planned to open an account today\nand deposit these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:11.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My intent was to let the interest from\nthe deposit accrue in the account.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:14.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I see that you\nare not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:20.81,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You leave me no choice, then.\NI shall try another bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:23.40,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please! W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.07,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:32.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lucien sure is a go-getter, coming over to talk\nbusiness with your father so early in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:35.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a child,\naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:38.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you actually\nadmire a guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"A guy like him"?\NHe's our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:45.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never thought of him\nas a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.75,0:10:48.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've been together\nsince we were kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:56.18,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That "friend" of ours\nis sleeping with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:03.90,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We are agreed, then. I will deposit these\nin your account right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.44,0:11:08.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I shall send over a servant later\nto pick up my first loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.28,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:13.11,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Incidentally, it has recently\ncome to my attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:16.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that you own the finest horse\nin all of Paris, Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:19.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you have an interest\nin horses, Count?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,English thoroughbreds\nin particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:26.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The thought had occurred to me\nto purchase it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Name your price.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.55,0:11:33.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:37.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That horse belongs to my wife.\NI have no intention of selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:43.56,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For the right price,\neverything is for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:47.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I should think that you would\Nknow that better than anyone, Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:02.41,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! Monsieur Danglars\nhas sold Madame's horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.62,0:12:03.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He sold Eclipse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:05.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mademoiselle!\NJust now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.54,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're going\nto fight again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:11.76,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur Danglars said that he was offered\na huge sum. He seemed very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NYou're interrupting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.77,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry, Count. This is my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.39,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Count of Monte Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:30.19,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where is my horse!\NWhere is my Eclipse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:32.69,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to discuss\nthis with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count, if you would kindly\nexcuse us for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:37.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You sold Eclipse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:42.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your voice down!\NLook, don't let this shock you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:47.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That horse was worth 5.8 million Francs,\nand the Count bought him for 20 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.67,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eclipse was my horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.55,0:12:53.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, that horse\nwas worth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about\nthe money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:59.05,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I promised Madame Villefort\Nthat she could use him tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have lots of\nother horses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:03.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to use any horse\nbut Eclipse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:05.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get in there and cancel\nthe deal this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.52,0:13:10.86,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You had no right to sell\nmy horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:18.74,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My good Baroness, if I have upset a beautiful\nlady such as yourself, I must apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:23.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I had thought that if I offered 60 million,\nyou would find the amount satisfactory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:29.33,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But we each have things that are so precious\nto us that a price cannot be put upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:34.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please pardon my ineptitude at failing\Nto take that into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:37.26,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...\NThat's quite all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:41.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But just a moment... Did I hear\nyou say 60 million just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.22,0:13:46.22,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, Madame. I offered\nto pay 60 million in gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:50.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. Please pardon\nmy silly question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:53.44,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I will\ntake my leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:57.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I shall respect Madame's wishes and\ndo my utmost to remedy the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:02.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Count...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:11.46,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Monsieur, were you planning to pocket a\npercentage of the profits, even from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.75,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.80,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You and your filthy lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:17.09,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my\nroom later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:20.97,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Albert,\nlet's go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we\ndo something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:24.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're always\nlike this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:34.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go any faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:37.82,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They're the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:41.57,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The worst family,\nand the worst father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:45.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the world\nto the Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:49.62,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know him\nat all, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:53.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If the price was right, he'd sell me off\nwithout giving it a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:06.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we stay here, we'll never be able\nto get out from under our parents' thumbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:11.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live\nmore freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:15.52,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I love the piano. I want to play\nall over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.02,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eugenie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:22.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live somewhere far away.\NSomewhere that my parents can't reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:28.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:33.00,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You and me.\NLet's leave home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:43.93,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:46.60,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:49.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back. I have to get\nfitted for my dress tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:53.85,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you wanted to leave here! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:30.68,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Valentine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:35.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?\NI thought you were coming with Eugenie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:40.98,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's true! He even comes\nto me in my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:44.03,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know\nwhat he said to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.24,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.45,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.58,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:17:00.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was given an invitation, too,\nbut I feel a bit out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:03.88,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.\NIt looks wonderful on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:07.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's a loaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:36.37,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought that the Prince's booth had\nbeen sealed up ever since that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:39.83,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 20 years since that\nhorrible accident, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.63,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that someone has put it\non permanent reserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:46.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's unnerving, isn't it? It's as if the\nlate Prince has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:48.84,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, let's stop talking\nabout such frightful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a handsome gentleman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:20.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the young lady\nnext to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:25.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but she's so lovely,\nisn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.18,0:18:32.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Albert, who is\nyour friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.06,0:18:38.89,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Madame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.98,0:18:40.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Don't make\nsuch a racket...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:44.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your horse, Madame!\NEclipse has returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:45.94,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:55.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A new set of box seats\nwas unveiled today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:18:58.04,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Monte Cristo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:18:59.70,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where are his seats?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:05.92,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's...\NThat's the late Prince's box!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:07.38,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning\nof this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:09.21,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been informed of\nany of the details, Monsieur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.79,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:41.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.42,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His Excellency the Count of Monte Cristo\nordered me to give this to Madame...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:50.17,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as both an apology and as\na getting-acquainted gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:55.47,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't know what to say!\NWhat a wonderful gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.93,0:20:01.31,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Deposit of 4.5 trillion dollars from\NVanderbilt Far East of Cygnus Alpha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:07.48,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Deposit of 328 trillion pesos from the Space Canal\NCorporation in the Union of Northern Sanctuaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.15,0:20:09.65,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Deposit of\N14.2 billion pounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.69,0:20:14.53,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...from Gravity Advanced Materials\Nof the United Central Emirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:16.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Deposit after deposit\nof foreign currency...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:19.49,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is being made into the Count\nof Monte Cristo's account.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:21.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell\nis that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:24.66,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he making\nall this money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:29.71,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the Count of Monte Cristo!\NWhat a magnificent man he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:32.30,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a magnificent man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:36.34,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle, that man is\nhiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:39.35,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I detect no\nsuspicious activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.68,0:20:44.43,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leave no stone unturned. Run thorough\nchecks on everyone he does business with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:45.64,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:55.99,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:02.91,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the man who...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.04,0:23:13.08,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hoping to help a friend with the\Nfeelings that he secretly harbors,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:15.25,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I go to visit Valentine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.29,0:23:17.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But what I witness\nthere is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:19.59,count fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,352)}Act 7:\NThe Secret Flower Garden
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.84,0:23:20.01,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, Act 7:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:21.55,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,..."The Secret\NFlower Garden."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.68,0:23:23.72,count main,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bide your time,\nand hold out hope!
